column1: Protocols: Traits were collected and measured following the methods of Cornelissen et al. 2003
Names of data takers: Harrison Lab
Column info: species, ecotype, height, specific leaf area, leaf area, wet weight, dry weight, leaf water content, carbon:nitrogen, nitrogen, carbon, and functional group

Definitions & Abbreviations: For species and ecotype: s=serpentine, n=non-serpentine, sla = specific leaf area, wgt=weight, lwc = leaf water content, CN  = carbon to nitrogen, N=nitrogen, C = carbon, fnc_grp = functional group
